  "id": "RAW_bb430072",
  "title": "英伟达还是放不下自动驾驶",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTAzMjc4MA==&mid=2650857988&idx=2&sn=99eda226070183e83456b7b8da760d21",
  "date": "2026-01-15 03:27:00",
  "author": "创业邦",
  "siteName": "创业邦",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/03KNO9Fib2w4gficvVhBKP6ic6h02Vxmrwdib2Qz5mrGcG3TGe4ibtAU04ic07BiaQm70dQMGHtoJibqAFmnypM5lhG1fg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"305\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"307\" data-imgfileid=\"503374336\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0f75c691&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2F03KNO9Fib2w4gficvVhBKP6ic6h02Vxmrwdib2Qz5mrGcG3TGe4ibtAU04ic07BiaQm70dQMGHtoJibqAFmnypM5lhG1fg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mkdpvtna244x\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkdpwcgk70c\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">来源丨远川科技评论</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（ID：</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">kechuangych</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">）</span></span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mkdpwcgkj87\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">作者丨</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">何律衡</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkdpwcgk1me7\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图源丨AI制作</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx13ne\">2026年第一个星期，车企牛马们收到了黄仁勋的开年大礼包。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dxw6a\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">刚刚结束的CES展，英伟达早早宣布没有新显卡发布，同时掏出了面向数据中心的</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">Rubin平台</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">和面向自动驾驶的VLA大模型</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">Alpamayo</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"2752\" data-height=\"1536\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"314\" data-imgfileid=\"100012468\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=db1cde96&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FSb3VkTngia9x5Dy46q3Tv9cZwEDCZy8ordAMCqlFKEyFeqlueKyibVyX4Lp7hfJiahEF3Pk6uiaw8mu2qKAwhNXfzw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D1\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mketvcv49he\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mketvcvqcps\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">2026 CES英伟达展台</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dxtvc\">VLA即Vision-Language-Action（视觉-语言-行动），具体在自动驾驶中，模型会将传感器数据先变成语言和符号，再通过推理形成决策交由车辆执行。好处是理解能力强，有可解释的推理痕迹，避免了黑箱情况。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx1y4w\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">去年，VLA接棒BEV和端到端，是自动驾驶领域当之无愧的年度热词。理想、小鹏、Momenta、地平线等企业都有类似技术方案。英伟达的</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">Alpamayo</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">则是首个开源的VLA大模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx1dgr\">作为英伟达汽车业务负责人，吴新宙在采访中表示，Alpamayo与特斯拉FSD“非常接近”，在一对一测试中，内部接管率处于同一水平[1]。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx19rc\">看热闹不嫌事儿大的网友第一时间@马斯克，表示马总这下要睡不着觉了。6G网速的马斯克也在第一时间回应，说自己睡眠质量还行，并“真心希望英伟达获得成功”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.4009259259259259\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1186\" data-height=\"476\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"226\" data-imgfileid=\"100012465\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7f8353dd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FSb3VkTngia9x5Dy46q3Tv9cZwEDCZy8orITUlNmLUWjclQGFbzj13vJtyibicibibhJklphN2hgPUF0usiaqUkpZlemA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D2\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx8ih\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">关于英伟达与特斯拉之争，子弹还得再飞一会儿，但无论马斯克睡不睡得着，都不会改变一个清晰的事实：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">这一次，英伟达要对自动驾驶发起总攻了。</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zPEErlmM1icwAxnc0Bfu3icv2I49pcxADF7lYww8vNML5TkajhGu2m1NA/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"219\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"42\" data-imgfileid=\"502705851\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d0e93a19&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zPEErlmM1icwAxnc0Bfu3icv2I49pcxADF7lYww8vNML5TkajhGu2m1NA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></strong></p>\n  <h5 style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx11zn\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mketvy5qxpm\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mketvy5x12oz\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">大模型预制菜</span></span></span></h5>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dxp7f\">作为当前自动驾驶最热门的技术路线之一，VLA模型在英伟达发布Alpamayo之前就已经吸引了诸多势力押注。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx1bqs\">小鹏据称早在2024年就开始开发VLA模型，在Alpamayo发布后没几天，小鹏就跳过了第一代，发布了自研的第二代VLA模型。理想、长城、奇瑞等车企也选择了VLA路线。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx231s\">特斯拉虽然没有完全公开自己的技术路线，但从FSD V14的种种信息看，特斯拉也采用了类似VLA的技术架构。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx1why\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">早期的自动驾驶算法高度依赖人工补丁，工程团队要尽可能穷尽所有的路况，并写入对应规则，效率非常低。特斯拉的端到端方案大幅简化了架构，通过高强度的训练，实现</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">传感器输入数据-算法输出决策</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">的效果，不再依赖人为穷举。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx1xqm\">但端到端也有局限性。一是输入和输出的中间过程是个黑箱，没办法追溯；二是由于这种“黑箱化”，优化算法只能不断投喂数据训练，效果不可控。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx3xs\">VLA的思路是把语言模型融入中间过程，让算法的决策可追溯、可解释。相比端到端纯粹“模仿”正确的驾驶行为，VLA让算法有了自主的推理决策能力，效果更加可控。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dxwcb\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">英伟达Alpamayo的轰动性不在于VLA本身，而在于开源。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx1wuf\">VLA虽好，但好东西都不便宜。车企开发VLA模型有三大大山，一是高质量数据获取、二是推理能力的训练、三是算力与成本，总之就是成本高。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dxxb3\">英伟达Alpamayo相当于给车企提供了一套完整的底层模型，车企可以基于自有数据和需求微调，形成自己的技术方案。既降低了开发难度，又保证了算法差异性。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx15yi\">相当于英伟达提供预制菜，车企按照自己的需求调整火候和调味，翻炒加热即可“出锅”上车。按照英伟达自己的说法[4]：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx1qjw\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">Alpamayo并不是直接部署于车端的模型，而是作为大规模教师模型，供开发者调优、蒸馏，成为其完整辅助驾驶技术栈的核心基础。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx1te4\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">除了Alpamayo开源模型，英伟达还送佛送到西，附赠仿真框架</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">AlpaSim</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">用以闭环测试，以及包含超过1727小时驾驶数据的Physical AI开放数据集，预制菜、锅碗、燃气灶一应俱全，不失为另一个角度的“智驾平权”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.5157407407407407\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1830\" data-height=\"944\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"290\" data-imgfileid=\"100012466\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5b08c5ea&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FSb3VkTngia9x5Dy46q3Tv9cZwEDCZy8orBia2VDkoYHT8PNBSHVlJ2mdTuE68D5bsRR7fib3ozsdoIVUK2MdbKbKA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D3\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dxsk9\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Alpamayo（模型）+AlpaSim（测试）+ Physical AI（数据）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dxtib\">在CES展当天的媒体采访环节，黄仁勋谈到特斯拉FSD时依然是一通乱吹，“世界级标杆”、“表现完美”、“我自己都在用”赞美三连[2]。可惜马斯克并不领情，回应完自己睡眠质量的担忧后再次开炮，一边大夸特夸特斯拉的技术水平，一边嘲讽汽车行业：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx22vz\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">“英伟达为汽车行业提供了有用的工具，但汽车行业本身却鲜有作为。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.7833333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1164\" data-height=\"912\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"440\" data-imgfileid=\"100012464\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a98c48ab&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FSb3VkTngia9x5Dy46q3Tv9cZwEDCZy8orhxoGawyZWgQNO1DylmrIWk6yMaZyJJ0VlmRlqnAM4tSbdudvYDVaQQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D4\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dxfix\">不管马斯克是不是在借机升堂，他这句话确实也没说错。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zSsWdBUSJRaL8xxhHssPefRrhSRCKFFTvyO0oNl4HVrDTxA2PCXqv1g/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"42\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"42\" data-imgfileid=\"502705850\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9f561975&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zSsWdBUSJRaL8xxhHssPefRrhSRCKFFTvyO0oNl4HVrDTxA2PCXqv1g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <h5 style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx15zf\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">英伟达的心事</span></span></span></h5>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dxcud\">英伟达的汽车业务，远看像个宝，近看像根草。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx1sto\">从市占率来看，英伟达DRIVE系列是L2+及以上中高阶智驾多年霸主，Drive Thor量产拖延一度让头部车企新车发布节奏被集体打乱，地位超然可见一斑。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dxcwr\">但从汽车业务实际贡献的收入看，虽然增长不算低，但相比在数据中心市场的统治力，恐怕也没达到黄仁勋的预期。拿下高速增长的汽车市场，也是英伟达从小鹏挖走吴新宙的重要原因。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"1.2138888888888888\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1340\" data-height=\"1626\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"682\" data-imgfileid=\"100012471\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bd74a78f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FSb3VkTngia9x5Dy46q3Tv9cZwEDCZy8orFqFfOuibl9YBxOykeiaUa92bHrbOwl6iapWo4kE8UiaBbgKZEcwecDBTZw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D5\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"1.1212962962962962\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1340\" data-height=\"1502\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"630\" data-imgfileid=\"100012472\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6e8dfdb8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FSb3VkTngia9x5Dy46q3Tv9cZwEDCZy8ordFCeibibFhpNPAtbwZh8JwpvK2ibzstgvfAle77Txj4HyAMzztIrkel0w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D6\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx1s1p\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">作为一家“卖铲子”的芯片公司，英伟达在软件上的所有投入，都是为了更好的卖芯片。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dxq1a\">从游戏到数据中心，再到人形机器人，英伟达的思路都是给客户提供标准化的工具箱（如cuda）和开发环境，并将这些软件服务与自家硬件绑定，最终目的还是卖芯片。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dxhun\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">不过在汽车业务上，英伟达遇到了严峻的问题：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">卖铲子的人不会用铲子。</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx136r\">英伟达只卖芯片，具体的自动驾驶算法需要车企基于芯片自行研发。因此，英伟达汽车业务的大客户，一直是小鹏、蔚来这些软件、算法能力比较强的国内新势力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dxi3l\">但问题是，这些客户多少都有自研芯片脱离英伟达的心思，蔚来的芯片已经上车，小鹏的图灵芯片也量产在即。而大众、奔驰、宝马这些销量更高的老牌车企，基本都没什么自动驾驶算法的研发能力，就很难给英伟达提供订单。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx17ck\">而英伟达自己身为顶级卖铲人，对自动驾驶算法的研发也是知之甚少。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx20q2\">于是黄仁勋痛定思痛，既然老牌车企都不会用铲子，那就写一份详细的使用说明书，让车企在这个基础上发挥主观能动性。吴新宙跳槽来英伟达，做的就是这个工作。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx1c6k\">Alpamayo就是英伟达痛定思痛的结果之一，不会写代码，那就给一个代码模板，虽不能照抄，但改一改也能用。同时从硬件到开发工具，全部进化到“保姆式服务”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx1ims\">最新的DRIVE Orin/Thor硬件平台，不仅提供芯片，还提供完整的车载计算机硬件设计蓝图；物理级精确仿真平台NVIDIA DRIVE Sim，可以为企业生成合成数据、进行极端的安全测试。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dxvl4\">再加上最新一代数据中心芯片Vera Rubin、世界模型Cosmos，英伟达真正建成了一个“云端训练（Rubin+Cosmos）+车端推理（Thor+Alpamayo）”的智能驾驶工具链闭环，饭喂到嘴边，闭眼吃就是。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"675\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"100012469\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=df14498b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FSb3VkTngia9x5Dy46q3Tv9cZwEDCZy8or7HRHPpmDJynPOkI8iaicjRGcuUcJqjJdpbdPTBynjOWBB059BjibSEe4g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D7\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dxx4\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">英伟达智能驾驶形成了一个工具链闭环</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx1fdp\">Alpamayo的另一面，是英伟达在“标准化”和“定制化”之间的一次重新校准。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx12fs\">对英伟达来说，最理想的商业模式是销售标准化的芯片，这样毛利率最高，估值空间最大。一旦涉足定制化的算法开发，就成了干一个项目结一次钱的施工队。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx1xbl\">所以过去这些年，英伟达汽车业务的经营思路就是不断提升软件工具箱的丰富度，降低车企使用自家芯片的门槛，但坚决不亲自下场做车企的自动驾驶项目。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkesz2dx14xi\">Alpamayo就是这一策略的最新产物，英伟达宁愿研发一套开源的算法交给汽车行业，也不愿意自己当乙方。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0px 16px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"800\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"450\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"100012470\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a0683ad9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FSb3VkTngia9x5Dy46q3Tv9cZwEDCZy8orKj48sWlib00u9g92DVsedUUqKrlGtgfTT28hYciceelrtrJN8CndoeXQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D8\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -a